direction - Variable in class antworld.common.AntAction
One of the 8 possible directions.
Direction - Enum in antworld.common
To check all directions around a location (x0, y0), use:
for (Direction dir : Direction.values())
{
int x = x0 + dir.deltaX();
int y = y0 + dir.deltaY();
}

Most methods that expect a direction, if given null, will assume the current location is being indicated (deltaX and deltaY == 0).
disconnectClient() - Method in class antworld.server.Nest
DO NOT call this method from the mainGameLoop thread as client.closeSocket() sleeps for 100s of ticks to make sure error message goes through before breaking socket.
